<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="雜科聲德" xml:id="gsz0898a04shiWuJi"><lb
ed="T" n="0898a04"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0898a04"/><head><date from-iso="+0923-05-18" key="j20583162063308" to-iso="+0937-01-16">後唐</date>靈州廣福寺<persName key="A008808">無迹</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0898a05"/><persName key="A008808">釋無迹</persName>，姓史氏，<placeName key="PL000000042247">朔方</placeName>人也。<date key="j20301712031392" notAfter-iso="+0849-08-29" notBefore-iso="+0846-04-26">當宣宗御宇</date>，佛法<lb
ed="T" n="0898a06"/>中興。<date key="j20333682033751" notAfter-iso="+0856-02-13" notBefore-iso="+0855-01-26"><name>大中</name>九年</date>，年正十三，決志捨家，投白<lb
ed="T" n="0898a07"/>草院<!--找不到此地--><persName key="A019516">法空大師</persName>為弟子，操執密縝，拂攘囂<lb
ed="T" n="0898a08"/>塵。<date key="j20359372036290" notAfter-iso="+0863-01-26" notBefore-iso="+0862-02-07"><name>咸通</name>三年</date>，用賓于<placeName key="PL000000042189">京室</placeName>，得戒度於<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明<lb
ed="T" n="0898a09"/>寺</placeName>矣。凡於百藝，悉願遊焉。慕定林<persName key="A010051">威</persName>能畫，<lb
ed="T" n="0898a10"/><persName key="A002712">戴安道</persName>能琴，我則講貫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1247"/>之餘，兼而綜習。先是<lb
ed="T" n="0898a11"/><persName key="A013704">唐恒夫</persName>甞作鎮<placeName key="PL000000047167">朔方</placeName>，後於<placeName key="PL000000042189">輦</placeName>下相遇，以家<lb
ed="T" n="0898a12"/>僧之禮待焉。蓋知言行相高，復能唱導聞。<persName key="A013704">恒<lb
ed="T" n="0898a13"/>夫</persName>白兩街功德使，請隷<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName>。旋屬<persName key="A006571">懿<lb
ed="T" n="0898a14"/>宗皇帝</persName>於鳳翔<placeName key="PL000000042886">法門寺</placeName>迎真身，右<anchor xml:id="beg0898001"/>宣<anchor xml:id="end0898001"/>副使<lb
ed="T" n="0898a15"/><persName key="A013972">張思廣</persName>奏<persName key="A008808">迹</persName>充乎讚導，悅懌上心，宣賚稠<lb
ed="T" n="0898a16"/>厚。<date key="j20443962045496" notAfter-iso="+0888-04-10" notBefore-iso="+0885-04-06"><name>光啟</name>中</date>傳授佛頂熾盛光降諸星宿吉祥<lb
ed="T" n="0898a17"/>道場法，歸本府。府帥<persName key="A013474">韓公</persName>聞其堪消分野<lb
ed="T" n="0898a18"/>之災，乃於鞠場結壇修飾，而多感應。<date key="j20468932047631" notAfter-iso="+0894-02-13" notBefore-iso="+0892-02-06"><name>景福</name></date><lb
ed="T" n="0898a19"/>中，太尉<persName key="A013474">韓公</persName>創修<placeName key="PL000000047136">廣福寺</placeName>，奏<persName key="A008808">迹</persName>住持。皆以<lb
ed="T" n="0898a20"/>律範繩之，塞垣閒求戒者必請為力生焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0898a21"/><date key="j20556632056017" notAfter-iso="+0917-01-30" notBefore-iso="+0916-02-11">梁<name>乾化</name>丙子歲</date><!--梁<name>乾化</name>無丙子歲,應為<name>貞明</name> 二年 丙子-->，中書令<persName key="A013474">韓公洙</persName>奏署<persName key="A008808">師</persName>號曰<lb
ed="T" n="0898a22"/><persName key="A008808">鴻遠</persName>歟。<date key="j20590302059030" when-iso="+0925-05-01">後唐<name>同光</name>三年乙酉歲四月一日</date>，坐<lb
ed="T" n="0898a23"/>終于<anchor xml:id="beg0898sgsz1"/>丈<anchor xml:id="end0898sgsz1"/>室。筋骨如生，風神若在，蕃漢之人<lb
ed="T" n="0898a24"/>觀<anchor xml:id="beg0898sgsz3"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0898sgsz3"/>稱<anchor xml:id="beg0898sgsz4"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0898sgsz4"/>曰：「昔<date key="j19974111997993" notAfter-iso="+0758-03-21" notBefore-iso="+0756-08-16"><name>至德</name>中</date>當府<placeName key="PL000000047106">龍興寺</placeName>有高士<lb
ed="T" n="0898a25"/><persName key="A011240">辯才</persName>坐亡，遂漆布之。<date key="j20476322047985" notAfter-iso="+0895-02-02" notBefore-iso="+0894-02-14"><name>乾寧</name>元年</date>府帥舉奏，<lb
ed="T" n="0898a26"/>勅諡曰<persName key="A011240">能覺</persName>。今<persName key="A008808">迹師</persName>可不異時而同事哉！」<lb
ed="T" n="0898a27"/>中<anchor xml:id="beg0898002"/>書令<anchor xml:id="end0898002"/><persName key="A013474">韓公</persName>命工布漆焉。<persName key="A006575">莊宗</persName>朝軍府從事<lb
ed="T" n="0898a28"/><persName key="A013707">薛昭紀</persName>為碑頌德云。</p>
